            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%B1%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87%E6%AF%92%E7%8E%8B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%A3%E5%B0%B1%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%98%91%E8%8F%87%E6%AF%92%E7%8E%8B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳发现一口就致命的蘑菇毒王#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>近日，龙岗区疾控部门在龙岗区嶂背郊野公园又又又发现了咱们最不想见到的“老朋友”——“致命毒物”，被称为蘑菇界“毒王”的致命鹅膏，在梧桐山、凤凰山、银湖山、碧岭等地方都有它的身影。<br><br>卫子提醒，不想被毒菇“索命”，唯一的方法就是：野外的蘑菇，不采！不买！不吃！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcwof3qbu9j20j10j5q5l.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcwodsbacqj20rs1rdtn6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hcwodtkq9zj20v91zt11q.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
